.TH LIGHTNING-PEER-UPTIME-SKEWNESS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-uptime-skewness \- compute skewness of peer uptime distribution
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-uptime-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries listpeers and computes the skewness of the uptime distribution across peers.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with field \fBuptime_skewness_peer\fR.
